snippet.title: Arcade Legend - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Build and manage your own arcade in Arcade Legend. Play officially licensed arcade games with friends in VR and win tickets and prizes. Check out the latest trailer to see the game's recent updates including bowling, licensed DLC featuring the Big Bass Wheel, and Skee-Ball Extreme. Arcade Legend's next free update introduces axe throwing.
